<http://www.semanticweb.org/diniz/ontologies/2024/8/untitled-ontology-30> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/diniz/ontologies/2024/8/untitled-ontology-30> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionIRI> <http://www.semanticweb.org/diniz/ontologies/2024/8/untitled-ontology-30/1.0.0> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/diniz/ontologies/2024/8/untitled-ontology-30> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> "INT-ACT UÉvora Team" .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/diniz/ontologies/2024/8/untitled-ontology-30> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/license> <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/diniz/ontologies/2024/8/untitled-ontology-30> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "This ontology reuses and integrates the SKOS (Simple Knowledge Organization System) vocabulary for the organisation of domain-specific concepts, and builds upon the CIDOC Conceptual Reference Model (CRM) for the representation of cultural heritage entities and events." .
